n!\nlog file /tmp/logging\n\n!\nip forwarding\nvrf mgmt\n exit-vrf\n!\nfrr defaults datacenter\n!\ninterface lo\n no shutdown\n ip address 10.0.0.2/32\n!\ninterface eth1\n no shutdown\n description l1 -> spine [external]\n ip address 10.1.0.2/30\n!\ninterface eth2\n no shutdown\n description [Access VLAN red] l1 -> h1\n ! no ip address\n!\ninterface vlan1000\n no shutdown\n description VLAN red (1000) -> [h1,h2,l2] [external]\n ! no ip address\n!\ndo write\nCONFIG\nvtysh -f /tmp/config\n!\nexit 0\n"
